  "text": "González et al. try to reduce the register idle time that occurs whilst defining instructions are waiting to execute by proposing virtual-physical registers [CITATION_1] . They allocate a virtual tag to an instruction as its destination at rename and delay the allocation of a physical register until writeback.",
